{
  "text": "The cooling of a body area involves a complex of physiological responses that Cryotherapy is used to prevent muscle damage, ( Bailey et al 2007) either separate or associated to stretching in the stretching -spray technique [CITATION_1] . Cryoultrasound (cryotherapy with ultrasound) therapy has more scientific evidence in treatment of tendonitis thank in muscle injury [CITATION_2] .",
